{"tid":132422,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如何放低一個你好鐘意既人","createTime":"2017-02-23T22:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T17:35:55.000Z","uid":10605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c49405dc719b707a98995da127d52cc29aefac0a","tid":132422,"uid":10605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T22:59:06.000Z","msg":"同ex兩個月前散左 <br />\n但因為係同事日日見 仲好鐘意佢<br />\n但睇得出佢其實對我已經淡<br />\n最近因為某件事 講講下 <br />\n自己衰感性衝動 同佢講左自己仲好鐘意佢 <br />\n但當然佢不為所動 咁最後得我自己痛苦<br />\n想問下各位有咩情況下可以放低/忘記佢呢<br />\n利申唔搵水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8046665f11532f84f2e7e7e5e38573103fc5d784","tid":132422,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:08:26.000Z","msg":"將自己集中力放係另一個女仔"},{"pid":"f7fbccb81fa85d97b84391511a6632fa6d39298c","tid":132422,"uid":10605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將自己集中力放係另一個女仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係絲打黎 唔搵水泡between"},{"pid":"10a11744a44b849b0e438a3428ca89903210d0fa","tid":132422,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>將自己集中力放係另一個女仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係絲打黎 唔搵水泡between</blockquote><br />\n絲打唔可以將集中力放係另一個女仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad91a3ae19daf0973df18a5c14e5ca7c0bd020d","tid":132422,"uid":2165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:15:10.000Z","msg":"約多d朋友玩，時間長左你嘅感覺總會有不同<br />\n唔需要刻意忘記因爲愈想忘愈掛念<br />\n利申之前個ex用感兩年先完全放底"},{"pid":"5940fc79eb9b4a14218f72898dc55bdb1a5ffcf8","tid":132422,"uid":31675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>將自己集中力放係另一個女仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係絲打黎 唔搵水泡between</blockquote><br />\n絲打唔可以將集中力放係另一個女仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1c56ec044792ad9a30ecfed49a5826368e4c35","tid":132422,"uid":57607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:17:12.000Z","msg":"調轉毒撚有個女仔好鍾意<br />\n前幾日食飯見到拖住個mk仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd9a4452ef1c760467b514b067c7bb911b1185b","tid":132422,"uid":10605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>調轉毒撚有個女仔好鍾意<br />\n前幾日食飯見到拖住個mk仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都毒毒地絲打黎 <br />\n唔好俾我見到佢同果條女拖住出街 我怕我會崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fc90f26258bb8824eaeafad3e5906c385a908f","tid":132422,"uid":10605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>約多d朋友玩，時間長左你嘅感覺總會有不同<br />\n唔需要刻意忘記因爲愈想忘愈掛念<br />\n利申之前個ex用感兩年先完全放底</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實呢段時間都不斷嘗試約唔同嘅朋友 一兩個又好 一大班又好 甚至係想追自己既人<br />\n但係出到黎都會自己腦海中不斷諗起佢 <br />\n或者突然間好想喊 驚自己情緒影響到人 唉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb9233705c155d82af6cc65b7be85cb9103f641","tid":132422,"uid":53769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:27:00.000Z","msg":"慢慢從好愛好愛至心淡失望死心"},{"pid":"42e5e1584821190fd228c96d59159812dcd3c4e2","tid":132422,"uid":49912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:38:52.000Z","msg":"如果可以嘅話，轉工<br />\n<br />\n日日見真係好難抽身<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過等左一個人五年先放手 期間都唔知有無講過十句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8789b710dd38b02e05b552cb9edcf1a0d6de9d08","tid":132422,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T23:50:33.000Z","msg":"唔捨得啫<br />\n實會嘅"},{"pid":"b22ce1b2a578d42c70d5c11cf545417e38637a30","tid":132422,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"同病相憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896766fddab11ef6f0d7ec5010fb9e18837ffa71","tid":132422,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"轉工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf02829ce1593f39dd89a1ebe4306b6742e2824","tid":132422,"uid":10256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:43:22.000Z","msg":"轉工<br />\n望多眼都抽唔到身"},{"pid":"52ea948210759637b25dfb839bee4cdd4104f473","tid":132422,"uid":27763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T00:52:47.000Z","msg":"其實冇乜野，分左手既佢只不過係過客，無需重視"},{"pid":"1cc9eecf0497dca2a1ff758dfd1f619c6323f9d8","tid":132422,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:51:53.000Z","msg":"感情事無得夾硬黎，你做曬契弟都唔代表嗰個人會回心轉意。😞😞<br />\n<br />\n要放過自己，唔好咁執著，受苦嗰個只係自己。😢😢"},{"pid":"bec0459d7f999aa62a486dc06633b5fe8f9f5756","tid":132422,"uid":23218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"搵人傾計 瘋狂搵人傾計 仲會搵到個令你放手嘅意見"},{"pid":"6ac31eb89ea20eb64004289186926cb894fac95f","tid":132422,"uid":23218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵人傾計 瘋狂搵人傾計 總會搵到個令你放手嘅意見</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d9856d4cd05e2218b5095f3415c09ebb33653f5d","tid":132422,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:07:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eebbd52039749f7852bdf18925e5e45e62e7369d","tid":132422,"uid":86541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"去旅行 散心"},{"pid":"1db8df18549b2c0a75f0fcc722c17cd3dcd9df56","tid":132422,"uid":10605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果可以嘅話，轉工<br />\n<br />\n日日見真係好難抽身<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過等左一個人五年先放手 期間都唔知有無講過十句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔捨得佢 所以唔會轉工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c630625ab2b0c48f402f3c91f86d0e72784092ad","tid":132422,"uid":10605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有冇其他方法啊"},{"pid":"b05273d0a16f0e66459c61cec5edb51bcf88337f","tid":132422,"uid":10605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵人傾計 瘋狂搵人傾計 仲會搵到個令你放手嘅意見</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實已經瘋狂搵咗好多人傾計 聽左好多人嘅意見 一時三刻之下係會放低 但係之後日日見到佢 果種感覺好容易就會黎返 雖然我知道佢唔會鐘意我"},{"pid":"252c85e689cb027d2816aab21735f5eef92db2ca","tid":132422,"uid":12514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果可以嘅話，轉工<br />\n<br />\n日日見真係好難抽身<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過等左一個人五年先放手 期間都唔知有無講過十句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔捨得佢 所以唔會轉工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔轉工又點放低佢呀大佬"},{"pid":"4ed4435d765986420660096c80963aa1cdc4d2c2","tid":132422,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:15:22.000Z","msg":"憎恨"},{"pid":"1b5c51c48737dccf5bd8aeabd9191a341646e02e","tid":132422,"uid":49912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果可以嘅話，轉工<br />\n<br />\n日日見真係好難抽身<br />\n<br />\n利申：試過等左一個人五年先放手 期間都唔知有無講過十句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔捨得佢 所以唔會轉工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔捨得咪等佢當你SP玩到你殘再傷多你一次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58324bf3c24bd220958f0b550aca95c777431c0d","tid":132422,"uid":42561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"拍左幾耐？"},{"pid":"981b143789c5568c964a677183b306778a398a9b","tid":132422,"uid":10605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍左幾耐？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一段好短嘅時間 但真係鍾意佢 就算知道好多佢唔好嘅事"},{"pid":"990e78a5c9e3df385e9abe3005ffdf180e41a7a8","tid":132422,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T10:22:07.000Z","msg":"變性"},{"pid":"4dfc8a702e2475e14e5e182323befede702c640b","tid":132422,"uid":3632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"你個CASE 都好慘<br />\n同事日見夜見<br />\n避無可避<br />\n<br />\nI know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a02d1b7ed3764287178ba97c782465d1c5f99f","tid":132422,"uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"一句講哂，時間<br />\n真心 時間係可以沖淡一切<br />\n係成功沖淡之前 盡量搵啲野做下打發時間<br />\n等自己啲時間易過啲<br />\n<br />\n利申 以前都試過同同學分手 （中學，仲要同班）<br />\n<br />\n加油絲打"},{"pid":"c471c55032ac7fbf4c195ff8cabdd888dccefa96","tid":132422,"uid":26280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"認真轉工啦<br />\n我都係忍左半年終於走左<br />\n果段時間又係因為工作關係一定會講野同wtsapp<br />\n睇住佢對我變到要做野被迫同我接觸咁 真係好辛苦<br />\n就算d pt同佢講野佢都識笑<br />\n我呢 我諗我走左之後佢肯定好開心終於見我唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8008bc6fd223589038e8678463f585fcf52b75d5","tid":132422,"uid":10605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T08:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真轉工啦<br />\n我都係忍左半年終於走左<br />\n果段時間又係因為工作關係一定會講野同wtsapp<br />\n睇住佢對我變到要做野被迫同我接觸咁 真係好辛苦<br />\n就算d pt同佢講野佢都識笑<br />\n我呢 我諗我走左之後佢肯定好開心終於見我唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></